    <h1 class="projects-page-tut"> How to use riceCAD to build projects in Minecraft</h1>
    <p></p>
    <p class="projects-page-tut">
        The main functionality provided with the riceCAD website is to import projects built on this website directly
        into Minecraft with the use of mods. There are a few specific things you'll need in order for this to work:</p>
    <ul>
    <li> Minecraft Java Edition (with mods enabled)</li>
    <li> <a href="https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/opencomputers">OpenComputers</a> Minecraft Mod</li>
    <li> riceBUILD program (coming soon!)</li>
    </ul>

</div>

